  "notes": [
    "This paper presents a computational method for identifying genetic interactions in cancer, extending beyond traditional synthetic lethality to include synthetic dosage lethality and tumor suppressor gene complexes.",
    "The gMIS approach integrates metabolic and regulatory networks to predict lethal genetic interventions involving both gene knockouts and knock-ins.",
    "Validation was performed using DepMap data and various cancer cell line databases."
  ]
